Tandis que Lili <mod type="corr"><orig>obs<mod type="del" stage="" who="P"><del>è</del></mod><mod type="add" stage="" who="P"><add>e</add></mod>rv<mod type="del" stage="" who="P"><del>er</del></mod><mod type="add" stage="" who="P"><add>ait</add></mod></orig><reg>observait</reg></mod> le terrain vague, <mod type="del" stage="" who="P"><del>quand</del></mod>
