Quand <mod type="corr"><orig>elle<mod type="add" stage="" who="P"><add>s</add></mod></orig><reg>elles</reg></mod> <mod type="corr"><orig>vit<mod type="add" stage="" who="P"><add>vient</add></mod></orig><reg>virent</reg></mod> que derrière cette porte <mod type="corr"><orig>ce</orig><reg>se</reg></mod> tenait <mod type="corr"><orig>de-Ł-bout</orig><reg>debout</reg></mod> <mod type="subst"><del><mod type="del" stage="" who="P"><del>entrain</del></mod></del><add stage="" who="P">en train</add></mod> <mod type="corr"><orig>d'avanç<mod type="del" stage="" who="P"><del>ait</del></mod><mod type="add" stage="" who="P"><add>er</add></mod></orig><reg>avancer</reg></mod> lentement, mais vigoureusement
